建築物倒塌或傾斜。"},{"pid":"e6d1b446c9bbb6111099b7f51da5f26072899855","tid":551922,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T10:42:14.000Z","msg":"2018年2月9日，環球股市一周內第三次大跌，道指瀉1032點。香港股市再成亞洲區墳場，全日跌943點，90%股份(約1700)下跌，總結一周累跌3646點(約11%)。"},{"pid":"8b9250cde16b297de64cb4179abbe60fd99d255b","tid":551922,"uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T10:54:44.000Z","msg":"日日都有大事發生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n選擇性講"},{"pid":"5c193d8d38cda1b1cfef2fae6eb618423b319571","tid":551922,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T14:08:10.000Z","msg":"2018年2月10日，香港大埔公路發生開埠以來第二宗嚴重車禍，一架雙層巴士懷疑轉彎時車速過快造成翻側，事件造成18人當場死亡，1人送院後不治，9人危殆，66人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n2018年2月11日，俄羅斯一架有65名乘客及6名機組人員的客機起飛後不久墜毀。"},{"pid":"c12cc2e7cfc8bf33f120bf7cac3127e48fd8d819","tid":551922,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:17:55.000Z","msg":"2018年2月19日，前新華社香港分社副社長張浚生病逝，享年82歲。"},{"pid":"f670ad12a9003657a6288dda0f1b40a2fe521ca3","tid":551922,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17acdb801775f55b336668dd063b8010a05d94f3","tid":551922,"uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T08:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/06/151107_be3423b674b25223cff584a37bc4b3a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F06%2F151107_be3423b674b25223cff584a37bc4b3a4.png&h=e22d6f6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:33:52.000Z","msg":"藍斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3138a359cc146587ca3bb19bf749709beee43d3b","tid":551922,"uid":63113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T04:00:49.000Z","msg":"2018年3月9日，阿仙奴歐霸盃十六強賽事，艾朗藍斯在下半場突破越位陷阱，再扭過意大利鋼門明日之星當拿隆馬輕鬆射入網窩，協助球隊擴大優勢至2:0，最後亦以相同比數完場。<br />\n<br />\n2018年3月14日，著名物理學權威專家霍金去世，享年76歲。"},{"pid":"ac4f2e843d16da4ce1931f4d3a1bcb05a2e48c11","tid":551922,"uid":76845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f670ad12a9003657a6288dda0f1b40a2fe521ca3","tid":551922,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17acdb801775f55b336668dd063b8010a05d94f3","tid":551922,"uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T08:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/06/151107_be3423b674b25223cff584a37bc4b3a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F06%2F151107_be3423b674b25223cff584a37bc4b3a4.png&h=e22d6f6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:33:52.000Z","msg":"藍斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T04:16:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bce6844336a09e8844730bf56abc9c8f182efe0","tid":551922,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T06:09:46.000Z","msg":"2018年3月15日，香港沙田廣林苑槍擊案，一名醉酒男子奪去前來調停糾紛的警用配鎗槍，並連開多發子彈，兩名警員中槍送院。"},{"pid":"3eba2ef2ad1d0ea45d1acc5f30499dc348e86d05","tid":551922,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T06:16:10.000Z","msg":"連鎖蝶變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}